This is the notes for FileInputs

What if we wanted to allow the user to select one or more files?

to do this we set input to the type of "file"
this allows us to go ti the hard drive and select files 

here are some attributes we need to know about 
    - multiple
        * this allows the user to select multiple files 
    - accept
        * this allows use to tell the user what kind of files we can accept